snippet.textDisplay: This was so infectious and so awesome! Gurdas Maan is a living legend and Daljit was an excellent foil in this song. I think it is criminal that this is Gurdas Maan's first song in Coke Studio. He should have at least one every year. I look forward to new age interpretations of his classic hits. Missing Hans Raj Hans as well. He also has just one song in Coke Studio... though what an emotional one it is! Check it out!
